
CYBERCHRIST
===========
Static blog generator tool prayers.


HOW IT WORKS
------------
Panda copies all files from given source path to given destination.
Files ending with:
.html get ...
.css get ...
.js get ...


CONFIG FILES
------------
Config files most be textfiles with the name '_config' and reside and the source directory.
If no file found a default configuration will get used.
In this file you can specify key value pairs with the following known keys:
url	: The http url of the website
src	: The local source path
out	: The local destination path


USAGE
-----
panda ?[source path] ?[custom_config_file] ?[destinitation path]
#panda ?[source path] ?[destinitation path]
